volumes:
- name: shared-storage
  hostPath:
    path: /data/shared
    type: Directory

| Type                | Meaning                      |
| ------------------- | ---------------------------- |
| `""`                | no strict check              |
| `Directory`         | directory must already exist |
| `DirectoryOrCreate` | create if missing            |
| `File`              | file must exist              |
| `FileOrCreate`      | create file if missing       |
